User Story 1:

As a user
I would like to be able to customize my profile
So that people viewing my posts can view extra information about me

User Story 2:

As an administrator
I want to ensure that I always have access to the control panel
So that I can make changes to permissions

User Story 3:

As a user
I would like to be able to change my password
So that I can make sure no one else gets into my account